-tone"},{"s":42.96,"e":44.58,"text":"Aliens lean in with a silver grin"},{"s":44.58,"e":46.6,"text":"Say, “You been lost, but you still fit in”"},{"s":46.66,"e":48.48,"text":"Angels above me"},{"s":48.58,"e":49.68,"text":"Demons below"},{"s":50.2,"e":51.78,"text":"Jinn in the hallway"},{"s":52.04,"e":53.36,"text":"Tell me what I know"},{"s":54.2,"e":55.68,"text":"Souls in the rafters"},{"s":55.68,"e":57,"text":"Ghosts in the rain"},{"s":57.46,"e":59.28,"text":"All of them call me"},{"s":59.28,"e":60.94,"text":"Back to my name"},{"s":60.94,"e":62.06,"text":"All that, all that"},{"s":62.34,"e":64.8,"text":"Under the stars"},{"s":64.8,"e":66.032,"text":"All that, all that"},{"s":66.34,"e":68.26,"text":"Tattooed on my scars"},{"s":68.26,"e":69.556,"text":"All that, all that"},{"s":69.88,"e":72.16,"text":"Heaven and harm"},{"s":73.28,"e":75.28,"text":"All that, all that"},{"s":80.2,"e":81.96,"text":"Sleeping in my arms"},{"s":82.28,"e":83.96,"text":"At the soup line, everybody got a code"},{"s":84.24,"e":85.76,"text":"Bread in the bowl and a map to the road"},{"s":85.76,"e":87.4,"text":"A cop in a tie and a clown with a crown"},{"s":87.52,"e":89.1,"text":"Both keep staring like they know this town"},{"s":89.12,"e":90.8,"text":"An alien child with a paper plate"},{"s":90.98,"e":92.62,"text":"Asks if the end is just a change of state"},{"s":92.6,"e":93.94,"text":"I said, “Maybe, if the moon says so”"},{"s":93.96,"e":96.16,"text":"Then the walls lit up with a soft white glow"},{"s":96.2,"e":97.94,"text":"Ghost in the corner, she tapped my sleeve"},{"s":97.98,"e":99.76,"text":"Said, “Don’t trust the ones who promise leave”"},{"s":99.76,"e":101.56,"text":"A demon smiled with a borrowed face"},{"s":101.56,"e":103.88,"text":"An angel cried in a flawless place"},{"s":104.62,"e":105.84,"text":"Angels above me"},{"s":105.86,"e":107.04,"text":"Demons below"},{"s":107.78,"e":109.04,"text":"Jinn in the hallway"},{"s":109.44,"e":110.6,"text":"Tell me what I know"},{"s":111.08,"e":112.94,"text":"Souls in the rafters"},{"s":113.02,"e":114.28,"text":"Ghosts in the rain"},{"s":114.72,"e":116.56,"text":"All of them call me"},{"s":116.56,"e":118.06,"text":"Back to my name"},{"s":118.8,"e":120.08,"text":"All that, all that"},{"s":120.16,"e":122.3,"text":"Under the stars"},{"s":122.36,"e":123.46,"text":"All that, all that"},{"s":123.5,"e":125.5,"text":"Tattooed on my scars"},{"s":125.74,"e":127.1,"text":"All that, all that"},{"s":127.28,"e":129.2,"text":"Heaven and harm"},{"s":129.56,"e":132.64,"text":"All that, all that"},{"s":137.32,"e":140,"text":"Sleeping in my arms"},{"s":145.5,"e":150.12,"text":"I seen the old rites in a basement ring"},{"s":150.18,"e":153.7,"text":"Saw twelve moons rise from a paper king"},{"s":153.7,"e":157.28,"text":"Saw one face split into three, then four"},{"s":157.3,"e":160.7,"text":"Then the room went still like an open door"},{"s":160.8,"e":163.7,"text":"If you’re a sinner, if you’re made of light"},{"s":164.06,"e":167.3,"text":"If you came from ash or you came from night"},{"s":167.58,"e":170.72,"text":"If you’re here to stay or just passing through"},{"s":170.78,"e":176.84,"text":"The sky keeps room for the strange and true"},{"s":177.86,"e":179.2,"text":"All that, all that"},{"s":179.2,"e":181.32,"text":"Under the stars"},{"s":181.42,"e":182.56,"text":"All that, all that"},{"s":182.6,"e":184.6,"text":"Tattooed on my scars"},{"s":185.32,"e":186.3,"text":"All that, all that"},{"s":186.36,"e":188.12,"text":"Heaven and harm"},{"s":188.62,"e":189.7,"text":"All that, all that"},{"s":189.76,"e":191.62,"text":"Sleeping in my arms"},{"s":191.68,"e":193.28,"text":"Souls and ghosts"},{"s":193.28,"e":195.3,"text":"And names unseen"},{"s":195.4,"e":196.84,"text":"All that falls"},{"s":196.84,"e":198.92,"text":"Between the beams"},{"s":198.92,"e":200.46,"text":"Under the stars"},{"s":200.48,"e":202.24,"text":"I still believe"},{"s":202.24,"e":204.02,"text":"There’s room for you"},{"s":204.02,"e":206.08,"text":"And room for me"}],"duration":222.72,"source":"whisper-aligned","generatedAt":"2026-06-01T00:48:29.505Z","stats":{"whisperWords":447,"polishedWords":450,"matched":393,"matchRate":0.873}}